verses.verse: Rejoice <S%H7442><s%> in <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, O ye <S%H6662>righteous<s%>: <S%H8416>Praise<s%> is <S%H5000>comely<s%> for the <S%H6662>upright<s%>.
Give <S%H3034>thanks<s%> unto <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> with the <S%H3658>harp<s%>: <S%H2167>Sing<s%> praises unto him with the <S%H5035>psaltery<s%> of ten <S%H6218>strings<s%>.
Sing <S%H7891><s%> unto him a <S%H2319>new<s%> <S%H7892>song<s%>; <S%H5059>Play<s%> <S%H3190>skilfully<s%> with a loud <S%H8643>noise<s%>.
For the <S%H1697>word<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> is <S%H3477>right<s%>; And all his <S%H4639>work<s%> is done in <S%H530>faithfulness<s%>.
He <S%H157>loveth<s%> <S%H6666>righteousness<s%> and <S%H4941>justice<s%>: The <S%H776>earth<s%> is <S%H4390>full<s%> of the <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>.
By the <S%H1697>word<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> were the <S%H8064>heavens<s%> <S%H6213>made<s%>, And all the <S%H6635>host<s%> of them by the <S%H7307>breath<s%> of his <S%H6310>mouth<s%>.
He <S%H3664>gathereth<s%> the <S%H4325>waters<s%> of the <S%H3220>sea<s%> together as a <S%H5067>heap<s%>: He layeth <S%H5414>up<s%> the <S%H8415>deeps<s%> in <S%H214>store-houses<s%>.
Let all the <S%H776>earth<s%> <S%H3372>fear<s%> <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>: Let all the <S%H3427>inhabitants<s%> of the <S%H8398>world<s%> stand in awe of <S%H1481>him<s%>.
For he <S%H559>spake<s%>, and it was <S%H6680>done<s%>; He commanded, and it stood <S%H5975>fast<s%>.

Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> <S%H6331>bringeth<s%> the <S%H6098>counsel<s%> of the <S%H1471>nations<s%> to <S%H6331>nought<s%>; He <S%H5106>maketh<s%> the <S%H4284>thoughts<s%> of the <S%H5971>peoples<s%> to be of no <S%H5106>effect<s%>.
The <S%H6098>counsel<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> <S%H5975>standeth<s%> fast for <S%H5769>ever<s%>, The <S%H4284>thoughts<s%> of his <S%H3820>heart<s%> to <S%H1755>all<s%> <S%H1755>generations<s%>.
Blessed <S%H835><s%> is the <S%H1471>nation<s%> whose <S%H430>God<s%> is <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, The <S%H5971>people<s%> whom he hath <S%H977>chosen<s%> for his own <S%H5159>inheritance<s%>.
Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> <S%H5027>looketh<s%> from <S%H8064>heaven<s%>; He <S%H7200>beholdeth<s%> all the <S%H1121>sons<s%> of <S%H120>men<s%>;
From the <S%H4349>place<s%> of his <S%H3427>habitation<s%> he <S%H7688>looketh<s%> forth Upon all the <S%H3427>inhabitants<s%> of the <S%H776>earth<s%>,
He that <S%H3335>fashioneth<s%> the <S%H3820>hearts<s%> of them <S%H3162>all<s%>, That <S%H995>considereth<s%> all their <S%H4639>works<s%>.

There is no <S%H4428>king<s%> <S%H3467>saved<s%> by the <S%H7230>multitude<s%> of a <S%H2428>host<s%>: A mighty <S%H1368>man<s%> is not <S%H5337>delivered<s%> by <S%H7230>great<s%> <S%H3581>strength<s%>.
A <S%H5483>horse<s%> is a vain <S%H8267>thing<s%> for <S%H8668>safety<s%>; Neither doth he <S%H4422>deliver<s%> any by his <S%H7230>great<s%> <S%H2428>power<s%>.
Behold <S%H5869><s%>, the eye of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> is upon them that <S%H3373>fear<s%> <S%H3176>him<s%>, Upon them that hope in his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%>;
To <S%H5337>deliver<s%> their <S%H5315>soul<s%> from <S%H4194>death<s%>, And to keep them <S%H2421>alive<s%> in <S%H7458>famine<s%>.
Our <S%H5315>soul<s%> hath <S%H2442>waited<s%> for <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>: He is our <S%H5828>help<s%> and our <S%H4043>shield<s%>.
For our <S%H3820>heart<s%> shall <S%H8055>rejoice<s%> in <S%H982>him<s%>, Because we have trusted in his <S%H6944>holy<s%> <S%H8034>name<s%>.
Let thy <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%>, O <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, be upon <S%H3176>us<s%>, According as we have hoped in thee.
